Package: llamacppR
Type: Package
Title: Ellmer-Native llama.cpp Chats for R
Version: 0.1.2
Authors@R:
    person("Alex", "Kraieski", email = "arkraieski@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides an ellmer-style chat interface backed by native
    llama.cpp inference. The package vendors llama.cpp, exposes a
    chat_llamacpp() constructor for local GGUF models, supports token
    streaming, basic tool-calling loops, and helpers for downloading a
    curated default model.
